<para style="p">For the chief musician. A psalm of David the servant of Yahweh.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Sin speaks like an oracle in the heart of the wicked man;</para>

<para style="q1">there is no fear of God in his eyes.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />For he comforts himself,</para>

<para style="q1">thinking that his sin will not be discovered and be hated.</para>
